org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.util

Interface SliceElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompactedSliceElement

    public interface SliceElement
    SliceElement is a single position of a read contained in a Slice. Each read in the slice contributes a base, quality value, and direction.
    Author:
    dkatzel

    • Method Detail

      • getId

        String getId()
        Get the Id of this element. Each element in a single Slice must have a different Id, although SliceElements from different Slices can have the same Id. This Id is usually the read Id.
        Returns:
        the Id of this slice element.
